cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with the optimization of coordinated beamforming in a multiuser downlink CoMP system, which involves signal processing, wireless communication, and optimization. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves system-level optimization and control, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper uses simulation results to evaluate the proposed method, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
